headline: Comcast Opens New Lift Zone for Aiken Veterans in Aiken, South Carolina
summary: Comcast has teamed up with American Legion Post 26 to launch a new Lift Zone in Aiken, South Carolina, aimed at enhancing digital literacy and expanding access to technology for local residents. Comcast Lift Zones provide free, high-capacity WiFi in trusted community spaces nationwide, helping individuals access online resources, participate in virtual learning, and strengthen their computer skills. headline: RBC starts Comcast with a neutral view amid broadband competition
summary: Investing.com -- RBC Capital Markets started coverage of Comcast Corp with a Sector Perform rating and $38 price target, saying company’s solid execution has not been able to offset intense competitive pressures in broadband. The brokerage also said there was a lack of near-term growth drivers.
